
'''Talkr, text-to-speech podcasting software'''


URL = http://www.talkr.com

"Talkr is inviting bloggers to convert their text-only English-language blogs into podcasts using Talkr's free podcasting tool. The initial setup takes about 10 minutes, and the podcasts require no ongoing effort. Talkr takes text-only blogs and converts them into audio files," explains Chris Brooks, CEO of Talkr.com."
